MARITIME SAFETY INFORMATION WEBSITE.
1. DNC VDU UPDATED LIBRARIES AND PATCHES ARE UNRELIABLE ON
   NIPRNET AND WWW WEBSITES. FOR DNC VDU PATCH UPDATES,
   USE THE SIPRNET WEBSITE ONLY. FOR DNC VDU UPDATED
   LIBRARIES, DOWNLOAD INDIVIDUAL LIBRARIES ON THE SIPRNET
   WEBSITE ONLY. DO NOT USE MULTIPLE FILE DOWNLOAD OPTION.
2. CANCEL HYDROARC 285/14.
